race.comment: ZIPPER ON TIME (3) sizzled around this track over 515m in 29.28 for a 5 length success. In winning form and can measure up again. DASHING SLAY (4) is a well performed dog and winner of 10 races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (29.70). Has never been out of the money in six starts this course and distance. Is yet to miss the placings from this draw, including three wins, from six starts. Expected to be in this for a long way. PAW ZURI (6) lit up the clock in 29.24 when winning a Special conditions H over 515m at this track last start. Top win latest and can measure up again. PAW GERTRUDE (2) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.

runners.name: Dashing Slay
